            "chapterTitle": "Supplications in Funeral Prayers",
            "urn": 1608710,
            "body": "<p>Abu Hurairah (May Allah be pleased with him) reported: I heard the Messenger of Allah (\ufdfa) saying: \"When you pray over the dead, make a sincere supplication for him.\"<br/><br/><b>[Abu Dawud]</b>.</p>",
